rows.label: qst00100103_msg0001
rows.name:
Ah! Thanks a lot, Kebikebi pass
watch duty to Rimurimu no problemo!

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0002
rows.name:
Rimurimu smash previous lateness record
of 7,691 seconds.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0003
rows.name:
Because this happen thousandth time,
Kebikebi plan to lecture him for three
days and three nights.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0004
rows.name:
But Rimurimu gave Kebikebi half of
delicious Cinnopon Roll, so
Kebikebi forgive him.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0005
rows.name:
Kebikebi not monster. Generosity of
Kebikebi wide as Cloud Sea.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0007
rows.name: Here is reward from generous Kebikebi.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0008
rows.name:
If you see suspicious activity
aboard Goldmund, please report
to Kebikebi or Rimurimu!
